三、參考書目 (Reference)[符合教學目標之參考書目]



中文參考書目
教科書:機率論 高立圖書 (2012)劉志尉 編譯 ISBN :	9789862801406參考書籍:1.劉仁沛等著 "統計與生活"臺大出版中心 20102. 鈴木香織、竹原一彰著"圖解　機率、統計"出版社：積木, 20123.謬紹綱譯，機率與統計，蒼海書局2013


英文參考書目
(Walpole & Myers & Myers & Ye & Johnson & Miller & Freund：Probability & Statistics for Engineers and Scientists 9/E) reference book:1.Dimitri P. Bertsekas, and John N. Tsitsiklis, Introduction to Probability, Athena Scientific2. Ronald E. Walpole et al., Probability & Statistics for Engineers & Scientists, Prentice Hall





